    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Divina gratie munere et superne virtutis aux[i]lio a faucibus demonice
                        potestatis eruti, ut nos misericors Dominus eterne patrie gaudiis faciat
                        quoeredes, scedulis amonitionibus crebrisque preceptis informa. Umde est
                        illut: Venite ad me omnes qui laboratis et onerati estis et ego vos
                        requiescere faciam. Et ne quis de via ad eum perveniendi vel qualiter ab eo
                        recipiendi esset facultas dubitare quod promisit, ipse certam ostendit
                        formula cum dixit: Dimictite et dimictetur vobis, date et dabitur vobis.
                        N[ec] itamen oc idem quod hdocuit scingniter quis agiere, ortatur ipse
                        alibit cum dicit: Vigilate quia nescitis die neque ora. Anc voce silicet ita
                        omnes deb[e]mus frequentissime meditare, quatenus semper pre oculis mentis
                        abeatur. Oportet denique singulis, qui se omnipotentis Dei misericordia uius
                        mundi divitiis vel quibuscumque temporalibus adiumentis noverint conlatus,
                        et i[i]s qui acepit ab eo quantumlibet illi cumferre cum gratiarum actione,
                        a quo sibi noscit cunta que habet concessa, quia regnum Dei tantum valet
                        quantum habet; quod ut credidi possit dominicis instruimur documentis, qui
                        muliere duo minuta devote offerente plus sceteris [om]nibus offerentibus
                        aseruit [ob]tulisset. <persName><name ref="Ademarius"
                            >Adamari</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Hieremias">Germie</name></persName> de <geogName
                            ref="#estates/210" key="#Comitatus"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitato</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Comitatus"
                            >Lucense</placeName></geogName> per la remissione dei suoi peccati,
                        mediante anc paginam offersionis, dispone delle rebus ereditatis (â€¦) in
                            <geogName ref="#estates/87" key="#Iudiciaria #Comitatus #City_territory"
                                ><rs key="#Comitatus #City_territory">comitato effundo seo
                                territorio</rs> di <placeName ref="#places/86"
                                key="#Iudiciaria #Comitatus #City_territory"
                            >Populonia</placeName></geogName>, ovvero di una <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >cascina et curte domnicata</rs> posta in loco et finibus <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Curtes" ref="#places/544">Kasalona</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Rivers">fluvio Cornia</rs>, <rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciaria</rs>
                        Populoniense, con cascinis domnicatis et massariciis e tutte le sue
                        pertinenze, in particolare terra qui est posita <placeName>ad
                            Oclisi</placeName> et in <placeName>Asca Germie</placeName> sive in
                            <placeName>Puticco vocitatur Pelago Teudolfi</placeName>. Offre questi
                        beni al <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/79"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di San Pietro</orgName> di
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/285">Palatiolo</placeName>
                        prope <placeName ref="#places/85">Montevirde</placeName>, eccettuando la
                        quartam portionem che per moriincap ha dato a sua moglie <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelinda">Rollinda</name></persName> e fissando una pena di 30
                        libbre d'argento. Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary #Judge">notaio e
                            giudice imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                            >Rodolfo</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/207">Campetroso</placeName>. <rs key="#Writer"
                            >Testimoni</rs>: gg. <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gotitius"
                                >Gottizio</name></persName> e <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Winizo">Winizio</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Sichelmus">Sichelmo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Daibertus/Talnitius">Taiberto detto
                            Talnizio</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Iudo"
                            >Iudo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Albo"
                                >Albone</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Daibertus"
                                >Taiberto</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bonitius">Bonizio</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Warimbertus">Warimberto</name></persName>.</ab>
